    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require a dedicated owner to bring it back to life. The exterior exhibits significant rust on the rocker panels and wheel arches, along with several noticeable dents and faded clear coat across the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears in the driver's seat and a headliner that has begun to sag. Mechanically, the car starts but runs rough, likely needing immediate suspension work and a thorough engine tune-up. It is a project car best suited for someone with mechanical expertise or for use as a parts vehicle.",
      "price": 6500.0,
