      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one and literally looks like it just came off the lot! No scratches, no dents, and the interior still has that fresh car smell. It drives like a dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. You won't find another one this clean! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
