      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an uncompromising 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black. This S54-equipped unit features an impeccably maintained 8,000 RPM redline, with a proactive double-VANOS rebuild and subframe reinforcement already completed to exceed factory specifications. The Getrag 6-speed manual shifts with surgical precision, paired with a fresh Sachs clutch and a perfectly dialed-in variable M differential lock. The chassis remains laser-straight, riding on OEM-spec dampers with zero fluid weepage. The interior showcases pristine Cinnamon Nappa leather with zero bolster compression or wear on the Alcantara steering wheel. This is a turnkey, collector-grade example with a documented service history that validates its mechanical integrity and showroom-standard aesthetics.",
